{"tid":1657589,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"冇壓測 供款都係唔能夠多過收入50%","createTime":"2019-10-16T07:09:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T01:38:56.000Z","uid":54423,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dc45e630612d1b83b8565b3b976badf75ad0a73a","tid":1657589,"uid":54423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:09:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/arjOOzi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FarjOOzi.jpg&h=dc89d4fe&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n只係冇左加3里嘅壓力測試，唔係話咩有80萬就上到樓。要買800萬嘅樓，做9成按揭要求月入有5萬7。<br />\n留意第4點<br />\n未能符合銀行壓力測試的首次置業人士亦可申請敘造最高 8 成或 9 成按揭，<span style=\"color: red;\">但其供款與入息比率仍須不超過 50%（上述（3）的情況例外</span>），而其保費會因應風險因素作出額外調整。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭呢啲時勢推出黎，一係想轉移焦點，二係想令有樓人仕關注資本升值，支持停止目前亂局，拉攏中間騎牆派。年輕人掛住諗買樓少咁啲人出黎，中層掛住諗賣樓移民又少咁啲人出黎，到時運動嘅momentum就會大減。今次又係分化人民嘅老套路，希望大家盡快focus番。仲諗買樓？輸你就一世。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"http://www.hkmc.com.hk/files/press_release/330/chi/Press%20Release_Amendments%20to%20the%20Mortgage%20Insurance%20Programme_Chi.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkmc.com.hk%2Ffiles%2Fpress_release%2F330%2Fchi%2FPress%2520Release_Amendments%2520to%2520the%2520Mortgage%2520Insurance%2520Programme_Chi.pdf&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVvcbRDcn212Q0H9cnoVtDxk%3D&h=42df7665\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkmc.com.hk/files/press_release/330/chi/Press%20Release_Amendments%20to%20the%20Mortgage%20Insurance%20Programme_Chi.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"160b76114bf3463385a6c62c1ddca6adeceecffa","tid":1657589,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:10:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zBif5mg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzBif5mg.jpg&h=44757529&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e66553d9b3acb38580af0077885fd9562a9aa92f","tid":1657589,"uid":254968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:23:59.000Z","msg":"柒婆搞